<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Super Luxor</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .paragraph{
                font-size: 25px;
                width: 280vw;
            }
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
        .image-end-1{
            position: relative;
            cursor: pointer;
            height: 340px;
            width: 380px;
            margin: 40px;
            box-shadow: 10px 10px 5px #aaaaaa;
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-image: url("/images/5f2d8a233e2d6a641d62c631_1634319553914.jpg");
        }
        .dark{
            background-color: #333;
        }
        .image-end-1-big{
            z-index: 111;
            position: absolute;
            cursor: pointer;
            height: 540px;
            width: 880px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-left: 400px;
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-image: url("/images/5f2d8a233e2d6a641d62c631_1634319553914.jpg");
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 15px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: rgb(37, 37, 37); 
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #333; 
            border-radius: 25px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: #555; 
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/hurghada/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div id="image-1-big" class="image-end-1-big invisible"></div>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Super Luxor</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        In capitala antica (Teba ) o sa vizitam complexul de temple din Karnak, templul  Reginei Hasepsud, Valea Regilor, Colosii lui Memnon , fabrica de Alabastru  ,pranz..fara bauturi (bauturile sunt contra cost)
        Plecarea  va fi in jurul orei 04: 30 in functie de hotelul unde sunteti cazati iar sosirea in jurul orei 21 : 30 in functie de hotelul unde sunteti cazati si de trafic.
                <br><br>
        Pret:<br>
        Adult: 55-50 €<br>
        Copil: 25-30 €<br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        duminica, marti si joi <br><br>
        Optional se poate face plimbare cu barca pe Nil contra cost.
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        In the ancient capital (Thebes) we will visit the temple complex of Karnak, the temple of Queen Hasepsud, the Valley of the Kings, the Colossi of Memnon, the Alabaster factory, lunch ... no drinks (drinks are for a fee)
        Departure will be around 04:30 depending on the hotel where you are staying and arrival around 21:30 depending on the hotel where you are staying and traffic.<br><br>
        Price:<br>
        Adult: 55-50 €<br>
        Children: 25-30 €
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        Sunday, Tuesday and Thursday<br><br>
        Optionally you can take a boat ride on the Nile for a fee.
    </p>
    <div class="images-section" id="images-section">
        <div id="image-1" class="image-end-1"></div>
    </div>
</body>
<script>
    const image1 = document.getElementById("image-1")
    const imageBig1 = document.getElementById("image-1-big")
    const body = document.querySelector("body")

    image1.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        imageBig1.classList.remove("invisible")
        body.classList.add("dark")
        image1.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    imageBig1.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        imageBig1.classList.add("invisible")
        body.classList.remove("dark")
        image1.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>